overview:
Ryan Johnstun, DDS provides high-quality and professional family dentistry services in Arlington and Darrington, Washington.

Our team’s commitment is to provide excellent Arlington dental care to families within our community. We do this by personalizing each individual’s care according to their needs. Our goal is to help you and your family achieve and maintain good oral health. We aim to listen to all your concerns regarding your dental health. We will carefully assess your oral health during your first visit. Part of our program is to explain your treatment options. We want to better understand your situation so we can give you the care you need. We will provide you with a caring environment coupled with friendly staff you can rely on. With our Arlington family dentistry services, your comfort is our priority.
